    "In the work [44], a supervised entity extraction Table 2 Parameter set Parameter Value Fine-tuning stage Batch size 10 Learning rate 3 * 10 -4 Lora r 8 Lora alpha 32 Lora dropout 0.1 NER stage Temperature 0.1 Top p 0.75 Top k 40 Beams 4 Max tokens 1248 Recommendation stage Temperature 0.1/0.5 Top p 0.75 Top k 40 Beams 4 Max tokens 1248method was proposed in the field of Catalyst (the entity label are material, product, control method and faradaic efficiency), and obtain 57.68% F1.",
    "In this work, the ontology is more complex and hard to recognize, in the entity label as catalyst, product and faraday efficiency, CataLM's modified accuracy (which also can be seen as F1) are 75, 85 and 90%, but it performs poorly in entity extraction for control method, cell setup, and the reason may be those entity are more difficult to understand and cause hallucinations in LLMs.We also conducted ablation experiments in this paper.",
